Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.43,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)\fs10\pos(330,191)}你有新郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜上所述  活版印刷和指南針…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及火藥合稱文藝復興時期的三大發明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於這些發明對歷史發展的影響有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢  打個比方說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如從21世紀中選出三大發明的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(256,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經連接裝置就必有一席之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  這是非常重要的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(208,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經連接裝置為人類社會帶來了資訊革命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵麵包兩個  奶油蜜瓜包一個  還有草莓優格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在午休時給我帶到屋頂上來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢遲到的話  就準備當沙包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別那麼害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是公共攝影機的死角  你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算啥啊  怎麼只有一個炒麵麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經賣光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連幫我們當個跑腿的都做不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  胖豬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天奶油蜜瓜包兩個和草莓優格五杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  不然就真的把你當沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最後的最終機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的最終機會…意思都重複了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能現在說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Direct  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接連接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪公主學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(340,328)}Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以教我製作虛擬角色的竅門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材質感總是表現不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色的光影要怎樣處理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊  是黑雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我興奮個什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的大人物怎麼可能會注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概就只有這個地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡的身手是多麼靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我才不需要現實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在這個時代還有實體的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有虛擬世界不就足夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快  我要加速得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是虛擬世界  還是現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超越所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達到無人能及的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極速！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你躲到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春午休不見了蹤影  害我找了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,152級！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分263萬！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  趕緊給我退出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼是我的自由  你少管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  你對我來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(321,328)}Link  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出連線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(327,328)}Link  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘技  強制退出連線  服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這裡可是男廁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你怎麼知道我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了  剛剛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  不如把他們的郵件交給學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以讓他們停學  但之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要和阿拓商量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別跟阿拓說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  我打算就這樣過完學生時代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  像我這種人你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少讓我為你做點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬鈴薯沙拉和火腿起司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是阿春你喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不道歉不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千百合哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Direct  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接連接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,166級？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我還有誰能打出這種得分？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明只剩這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs15}VR：Virtual Reality的簡稱，即虛擬實境。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是比VR遊戲的技術…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為自己能夠不輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你打出那離譜的分數的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想「加速」得更快嗎  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天午休時  來交誼廳找我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小哥是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道這裡是高年級生的專屬地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找他有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  能讓他過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個除了插到脖子上去還有別的用途嗎
