Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.81,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&90&\fad(500,0)\fs19\pos(487,161)}是否運行程式BB2039？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.81,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&90&\fad(600,0)\fs19\pos(351,242)}確定                     取消
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這不是情侶之間才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩你走這一趟  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}思考發聲：不動嘴唇，通過連線裝置對話的技術。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會思考發聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會  請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是精心設計的惡作劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上來說就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(394,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  我要向你的神經連接裝置…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送一個應用程式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.88,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\pos(385,166)}是否運行程式BB2039？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.88,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\pos(333,207)}確定                            取消
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦接收它  你的現實將完全毀壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再以一種超乎想像的方式重構
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即我的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)\fs19\frx20\fry-9\frz-16\pos(345,77)}文件下載 - 安全警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)\fs25\frx15\fry-6\frz-16\pos(501,168)}是否運行程式BB2039？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,400)\fs27\frx21\fry-8\frz-20\pos(282,231)}確定{\r}                          {\fad(1000,400)\fs23\frx-6\fry-10\frz-20\pos(282,231)}取消
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如現實真能就此毀壞  這正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫Brain  Burst的程式…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功安裝之後  我再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說安裝可能會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerated…加速世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然沒猜錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日的我在接受時  也考慮了將近兩分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為說服你而準備的台詞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都浪費掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  別給我裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油蜜瓜包和草莓優格  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫荒谷  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從有田那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是有些誤會  才把你從動物園…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到這所中學來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  你都說啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這隻胖豬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機已到  快喊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要看我的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來剛好被公共攝影機拍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正身處於Brain  Burst的程式功能下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加速」狀態之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(301,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們超頻連線者居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(311,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線者？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下周圍是靜止的  但事實並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個藍色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由多台架設於交誼廳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共攝影機錄得的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重構出的3D影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(351,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再借由神經連接裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓思考得以加速的大腦觀看影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速思考？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速的比率是平常的一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  現實的1秒相當於這裡的1000秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即我們能體會到16分40秒的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要運用這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是快要被打到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在致命的瞬間加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能利用龐大的時間把握現狀考慮對策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是絕對躲不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  別躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時更應該被打飛才對  春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要  這很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名學生通過躲進公共攝影機的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直得不到應有的處分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有著眾多公共攝影機的大庭廣眾之下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經中了我的挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是反擊的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…如果使用Brain  Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能打得贏他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能贏得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你已經得到超乎常人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(358,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為一名超頻連線者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會乖乖地接他一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的選擇很明智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  就要讓效果最大化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速狀態取消後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要主動地向後面跳開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是學姐不是在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過要讓效果最大化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自有打算  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  好好幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  只是擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過要獲取最大的效果了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣荒谷就不會再出現在你面前  永遠不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受這一拳辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後請你多多指教  春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(450,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到明天上學為止  都不能卸下神經連接裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.49,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\fs18\pos(447,185)}斷開與全球互聯網的連接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可以連上全球網路  一秒都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說午休的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你被那傢伙打到飛了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那時的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那時受的傷？沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微擦到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  還好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級的黑雪公主和你直連是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些  昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊  正要回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  我看了前些日子的劍道大賽的錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒  才一年級就已經拿到冠軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  運氣好罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也多虧阿千帶便當來為我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得那麼起勁原來是有了便當的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過阿春昨天不也吃了阿千手製便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送便當是阿拓的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿拓又怎麼會知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道把荒谷的事說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會送我便當
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  有個想看的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  下次見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被阿拓知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才趕走了荒谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  現實終究是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想飛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}飛往天空的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做了個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs16\pos(418,155)\frx-10}連接全球互聯網
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  給我午餐錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪  你還沒連線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加速…了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是3D影像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是久違的世紀末場地  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手還是個亮閃閃的菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超幸運的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  你卻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒大楣了！
